247
00:24:04,570 --> 00:24:06,520
Imperial Physician, hurry and save her!

248
00:24:06,520 --> 00:24:07,490
Yes, I will obey!

249
00:24:07,490 --> 00:24:09,270
Thank you, Your Imperial Majesty!

250
00:24:10,120 --> 00:24:11,690
Hurry!

251
00:24:29,160 --> 00:24:32,220
Imperial Physician Wang, how is it?

252
00:24:33,310 --> 00:24:36,840
Responding to Crown Princess Consort. A'Du's internal injury

253
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:41,580
has shattered her inner organs. Even with the best miracle drug,

254
00:24:43,700 --> 00:24:46,430
