255
00:24:54,130 --> 00:24:55,700
A'Du...

256
00:24:57,730 --> 00:24:59,350
A'Du...

257
00:25:00,870 --> 00:25:02,860
I am sorry.

258
00:25:06,060 --> 00:25:11,420
I am sorry. I should not have let you chase that assassin.

259
00:25:13,300 --> 00:25:15,830
It is my fault.

260
00:25:17,330 --> 00:25:19,300
I am sorry.

261
00:25:21,310 --> 00:25:23,180
I am sorry.

262
00:25:48,550 --> 00:25:50,960
[Eastern Palace]

263
00:25:58,500 --> 00:26:01,190
