264
00:26:01,190 --> 00:26:07,100
From this day on, without a pass to leave the palace, no one is allowed to leave the palace!

265
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:08,740
Yes!

266
00:26:27,500 --> 00:26:30,400
You all should not cry.

267
00:26:30,400 --> 00:26:33,180
If crying could wake him up,

268
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:36,390
