270
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:55,200
After you cry, your heart will be able to bear it better.

271
00:27:01,650 --> 00:27:03,170
Xiaofeng.

272
00:27:03,950 --> 00:27:08,000
Xiaofeng, people outside only know that

273
00:27:08,000 --> 00:27:10,900
you and Fifth Brother would frequently fight,

274
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:15,270
