287
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:31,690
He got stabbed instead of me.

288
00:31:37,500 --> 00:31:38,870
Li Chengyin!

289
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:43,600
- Your Imperial Highness!
- Li Chengyin, are you awake now?

290
00:31:43,600 --> 00:31:45,170
- Your Imperial Highness.
- Mother.

291
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,660
What are you trying to say?

292
00:31:48,570 --> 00:31:51,990
- Mother.
- Mother?

293
00:31:54,650 --> 00:31:55,730
Crown Princess Consort!

294
00:31:55,730 --> 00:31:58,830
Shi'en, hurry and ask for the empress to come. He's calling for her.

295
00:31:58,830 --> 00:32:01,990
