297
00:32:28,330 --> 00:32:30,220
Chengyin.

298
00:32:32,900 --> 00:32:34,990
Chengyin.

299
00:32:39,510 --> 00:32:43,700
Chengyin, my child.

300
00:32:45,500 --> 00:32:47,620
Chengyin.

301
00:32:48,760 --> 00:32:50,650
Mother.

302
00:32:53,560 --> 00:32:55,350
Mother.

303
00:32:56,310 --> 00:33:00,920
Chengyin! I am here. I am here.

304
00:33:02,620 --> 00:33:06,750
I am here. I am here, Chengyin.

305
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:13,930
Chengyin, my child... I am here.

306
00:34:16,390 --> 00:34:18,100
Imperial Mother.

307
00:34:39,300 --> 00:34:42,780
Crown Princess Consort! It's bad!

308
00:34:42,780 --> 00:34:45,480
A'Du... is on the verge of death.

309
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:48,120
Crown Princess Consort, hurry and take a look at her!

310
00:34:56,430 --> 00:34:59,970
Imperial Doctor Wang, how is she?

311
00:35:00,750 --> 00:35:04,920
Crown Princess Consort, I am afraid that Miss A'Du...

312
00:35:04,920 --> 00:35:08,780
I am afraid that she will not make it past tonight.

313
00:35:21,220 --> 00:35:22,750
Xiaofeng!

314
00:35:23,830 --> 00:35:26,390
Teacher, you're here.

315
00:35:26,390 --> 00:35:29,600
Such a big commotion happened in the palace and I was worried about you, so I've been waiting here all this time.

316
00:35:29,600 --> 00:35:32,720
Hurry and go see A'Du. She has severe internal damage.

317
00:35:32,720 --> 00:35:37,450
The imperial doctor said she might not be able to make it past tonight. You're the only one who can save her.

318
00:35:37,450 --> 00:35:40,360
- Hurry. Take me to her.
- All right.

319
00:36:05,400 --> 00:36:10,000
If you just cultivate in peace, do not deplete your essence and internal energy,

320
00:36:10,000 --> 00:36:14,040
do not suffer another huge trauma, you may be able to live longer.

321
00:36:14,040 --> 00:36:17,890
But if you use your nascent energy and hurt your heart's energy,

322
00:36:17,890 --> 00:36:20,410
then your outcome will not be good.

323
00:36:20,410 --> 00:36:22,890
You already died once.

324
00:36:22,890 --> 00:36:26,900
Your second life is starting to disappear.

325
00:36:26,900 --> 00:36:30,790
When you are done repenting and your heart's soul has been released from the guilt,

326
00:36:30,790 --> 00:36:34,000
by that time, your body

327
00:36:34,000 --> 00:36:37,590
will suffer from the pain of a thousand arrows piercing through your heart.

328
00:37:07,620 --> 00:37:13,780
Responding to Crown Princess Consort, A'Du's vital energy channels have all cleared up.

329
00:37:13,780 --> 00:37:14,900
That's great!

330
00:37:14,900 --> 00:37:17,340
I will return to prescribe some more medication.

331
00:37:17,340 --> 00:37:21,500
- As long as Miss A'Du can eat, she won't have any big issues.
- All right.

332
00:37:21,500 --> 00:37:23,610
I will take my leave.

333
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:43,900
Teacher, the imperial doctor said that A'Du is safe now.

334
00:37:43,900 --> 00:37:45,530
Thank you.

335
00:37:47,080 --> 00:37:49,490
I still have a favor to ask you.

336
00:37:50,190 --> 00:37:56,470
Since you can save A'Du, could you think of a way to save Li Chengyin, too?

337
00:37:57,220 --> 00:38:00,420
He's been unconscious for a few days already. He still hasn't woken up yet.

338
00:38:00,420 --> 00:38:03,020
The imperial doctors have no idea what to do.

339
00:38:03,700 --> 00:38:05,740
You're being too greedy.

340
00:38:06,480 --> 00:38:10,510
I saved A'Du because she's your best friend.

341
00:38:10,510 --> 00:38:14,200
Why should I save Li Chengyin? He's always bullying you.

342
00:38:17,310 --> 00:38:19,530
He is my husband.

343
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,220
Husband...

344
00:38:23,220 --> 00:38:27,500
He got injured because of me. If he dies,

345
00:38:27,500 --> 00:38:30,000
