346
00:38:34,170 --> 00:38:35,990
Teacher...

347
00:38:37,340 --> 00:38:41,970
The crown prince is suffering from an external injury. My internal energy won't save him.

348
00:38:45,270 --> 00:38:49,830
This is a medicine for external wounds. Go and try it on him.

349
00:38:49,830 --> 00:38:53,230
If he can live or not, depends on his fortune.

350
00:39:03,000 --> 00:39:06,580
